, Simulation der Pflegesätze bis zum Umgang mit Risiko- und Wagnisaufschlägen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aMEDICAL / Nursing / General.2bisacsh  aAltenhilfe.  aPflegesatz.  aVergütungsverhandlungen.1 aFloßbach, Christopher, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aSatzvey, Sebastian, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2022z9783110993134oZDB-23-DPM40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978374860598040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783748605980423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783748605980/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DPMb2022